     May 30 (Bloomberg) - Rafi Mohammed, author of "The Art of 
Pricing," says retailers should put themselves in their 
customers' shoes when setting price. Mohammed talks with 
Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."      (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:12
 